## 12) Immediate Questions (blockers → ask at once)

- Private MCP extensions required? Required transports/auth in production? Compliance constraints? Target platforms/runtimes? Contractual SLOs/SLA?

Acceptance Criteria (hard line)

- Zero capability, safety, or security regressions.
- All tests in §6 pass; perf meets thresholds in §7.
- Inventory and parity matrix complete and reviewed.
- Old MCP code fully removed or isolated behind shims with deprecation timeline.
- Rollback path verified in staging.
